# Template for .env.dev — copy to `.env.dev` (gitignored) and fill in.
#   cp .env.dev.example .env.dev
# Loaded by the `dev` Spring profile via spring.config.import. The dev profile
# has NO YAML fallbacks for the REQUIRED values — the app won't start without them.

